<P>A SHORT Hi&s;torical Account Of the &s;everal Kinds of WORMS Breeding in Human Bodies: EXTRACTED From the Writings of the mo&s;t Eminent Authors.</P>
<P>WITH A particular De&s;cription of their Symptoms, and the mo&s;t Approved Remedies for their Expul&s;ion.</P>
<P>By <HI>M. M.</HI></P>
<P><HI>LONDON:</HI> Printed by <HI>B. Mills,</HI> and Sold by <HI>J. Baker,</HI> and <HI>T. Warner,</HI> at the <HI>Black-Boy</HI> in <HI>Pater-no&s;ter-Row.</HI> 1716.</P>
