<P><HI>Scharff</HI>'s E&s;&s;ence for <HI>Worms,</HI> which expell'd a <HI>Worm</HI> of a very great Thickne&s;s.</P>
<P>&rx; <HI>Herb. Abrotan, Scordij Tanacet a Mj. Rad dictam filicis Zedoar. a</HI> lb<HI>&s;s fl Centuar Mj. Per&s;icor p. ij Co|rallin</HI> &ounce;<HI>i&s;s. &s;. Sancton. Coriand. a</HI> &dram;<HI>vj Bacc. Junip.</HI> &ounce;<HI>ij Myrrh. Theriac. a</HI> &ounce;<HI>&s;s. Conci&s;. Contu&s;. infunde in S. q. Sp. Juniper rectif. Tinctum quod e&s;t &s;eparetur; Novus Sp. affundatur; conjunctis liquoribus addendo Sp. C. C. &s;ale volatili impregnati</HI> &ounce;<HI>ij. f. E&s;&s;entia.</HI></P>
<PB N="52" REF="51">
